and policies chaired by departments and agencies of the Ministry of Health; Field trips at pharmaceutical factories or typical hospitals in Ho Chi Minh City. Ho Chi Minh. There are also specialized workshops of exhibitors.\n\nIn order to promote the Exhibition, the advertising and communication work has been planned, prepared and carefully carried out on a large scale. Organizers are expected to issue and send more than 30,000 invitations through such forms as e-mail marketing, delivery by post, fax, direct phone calls to the Enterprise, managers and researchers. , training, hospitals, clinics, health centers and professional officials throughout the country to participate in exhibitions and work visits at the exhibition. Exhibition information is available in specialized newspapers and mass media including television, print, radio and website.";s:6:"filter";s:1:"1";s:11:"panels_info";a:6:{s:5:"class";s:30:"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE";s:4:"grid";i:2;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:2;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"499dc39d-f8b6-4dd6-abf9-12cc4bb23bf0";s:5:"style";a:2:{s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";}}}}s:5:"grids";a:3:{i:0;a:4:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:3:{s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";s:14:"cell_alignment";s:10:"flex-start";}s:5:"ratio";i:1;s:15:"ratio_direction";s:5:"right";}i:1;a:4:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:4:{s:5:"class";s:5:"major";s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";s:14:"cell_alignment";s:10:"flex-start";}s:5:"ratio";i:1;s:15:"ratio_direction";s:5:"right";}i:2;a:4:{s:5:"cells";i:1;s:5:"style";a:3:{s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";s:14:"cell_alignment";s:10:"flex-start";}s:5:"ratio";i:1;s:15:"ratio_direction";s:5:"right";}}s:10:"grid_cells";a:3:{i:0;a:4:{s:4:"grid";i:0;s:5:"index";i:0;s:6:"weight";i:1;s:5:"style";a:0:{}}i:1;a:4:{s:4:"grid";i:1;s:5:"index";i:0;s:6:"weight";i:1;s:5:"style";a:0: