(588, 1, '2019-01-20 15:06:49', '2019-01-20 15:06:49', '<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">This morning, August 2, 2018, in Ho Chi Minh City took place the International Exhibition of Pharmaceuticals and Medical Equipment - VIETNAM MEDI - PHARM EXPO for the 18th time, the event was organized by the Ministry of Health and Ministry of Public Works. Thuong presided over.</span></span>\n\n<img class="wp-image-472 size-full aligncenter" src="http://medipharm.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/a.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="451" />\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Many modern equipment are exhibited by the exhibitors at the exhibition</span></span></p>\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">This is an annual event of the health sector to introduce advanced technology products of Vietnam''s Medicine and Pharmacy industry and the world, propagating policies and laws of the Party and the State on Health work. .</span></span></p>\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">With the theme "Join hands to protect, care and improve public health", the exhibition attracted 350 businesses from 20 countries and territories such as Vietnam, India, China, Taiwan. (China), South Korea, Malaysia, Japan, Germany, America, Singapore, Russia, ... The products are mainly exhibited on Machinery - Medical equipment such as consumables, laboratory equipment, measuring measuring and testing; </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Endoscopic equipment, operating rooms, family medical equipment, blood pressure, blood sugar, ...</span></span></p>\n<img class="wp-image-473 size-full aligncenter" src="http://medipharm.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/2_756408.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="450" />\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Representatives of the Ministry of Industry and Trade, Ministry of Health and other related units participated in the Opening Ceremony of the Fair</span></span></p>\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Speaking at the Ceremony, Mr. Nguyen Dinh Anh, Director General, Department of Communications and Emulation - Ministry of Health said, exhibiting VIETNAM MEDI - PHARM EXPO is an opportunity for Vietnamese organizations and businesses to seek partners, promote products, enhance experience exchange, seize investment opportunities, expand markets, enter into joint ventures and technology transfer to improve production efficiency, business, contribute real present a good strategy to take care of, protect and improve the entire people''s health.</span></span></p>\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">It is known that in addition to displaying products, this exhibition has an in-depth workshop on "Update and treat diabetes in the world and Vietnam", "The role of family doctors in prevention and detection early and treat diabetes "," Thinsulin Method: Weight loss, beauty, diabetes reduction "will help visitors access, understand the product and new features and treatments.</span></span></p>\n<p class="body-text"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">The exhibition takes place from August 2 to 4, 2018 at the Saigon Convention and Exhibition Center (SECC - 799 Nguyen Van Linh, District 7, Ho Chi Minh City).</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Vu Hanh</span></span></p>\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Post link: https://baomoi.com/350-doanh-nghiep-tham-gia-trien-lam-quoc-te-chuyen-nganh-y-duoc-lan-thu-18/c/27123757.epi</span></span>', '350 doanh nghiệp tham gia triển lãm Quốc tế chuyên ngành Y - Dược lần thứ 19', 'Phát biểu tại buổi Lễ, ông Nguyễn Đình Anh, Vụ trưởng, Vụ Truyền thông và Thi đua khen thưởng – Bộ Y tế cho biết, triển lãm VIETNAM MEDI - PHARM EXPO là cơ hội để các tổ chức, doanh nghiệp Việt Nam tìm kiếm đối tác, quảng bá sản phẩm, tăng cường trao đổi kinh nghiệm, nắm bắt cơ hội đầu tư, mở rộng thị trường, liên doanh liên kết và chuyển giao công nghệ nhằm nâng cao hiệu quả sản suất, kinh doanh, góp phần thực hiện tốt chiến lược chăm sóc, bảo vệ và nâng cao sức khỏe toàn dân.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '471-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-01-20 15:06:49', '2019-01-20 15:06:49', '', 471, 'http://medipharm.co/471-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
