(607, 1, '2019-01-20 15:35:19', '2019-01-20 15:35:19', '<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">The event was organized by the Central Center for Health Education and Communication, Vietnam Health Import and Export Joint Stock Company (VIMEDIMEX VN), Vietnam Exhibition and Advertising Joint Stock Company (VIETFAIR).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Speaking at the press conference to introduce the Exhibition on the afternoon of April 24 in Hanoi, Mr. Nguyen Dinh Anh - Director of the Department of Communication and Emulation and Reward (Ministry of Health) said that this exhibition is an opportunity to introduce to the people the Party''s policies and guidelines, the State''s laws on health work; new advances and achievements of domestic and foreign medical and pharmaceutical industries in pharmaceuticals and functional foods; medical equipment and supplies; technical and support equipment, health care products ...</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Thereby, opening up opportunities for domestic and international businesses to introduce products, exchange, seek business partners, expand markets, enter into joint ventures and transfer technology in the field. Health aims to improve the efficiency of health service production and business, contributing to the protection, care and improvement of people''s health.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">According to the Organizing Committee, this year''s exhibition is the largest exhibition ever, attracting over 410 units with 500 booths from 30 countries and territories such as India, Bangladesh, Belgium, and China. Czech Republic, Germany, Israel, Japan, Korea, Malaysia, Netherlands, Pakistan, Singapore, Sweden, Thailand, America, Vietnam ...</span>\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-513 aligncenter" src="http://medipharm.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/yduoc-600x400.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" />\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Main display products at the exhibition include groups of products: pharmaceuticals, functional foods; Medical equipment; Hospital - clinic; Dentistry, ophthalmology; Support and technical equipment, health care products; Chemical and analytical equipment; Beauty equipment and products; Medical tourism; High quality medical, health care services ...</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the framework of the Exhibition, side events organized during the exhibition organized by the Ministry of Health include: Specialized seminars, answers to issues of Pharmacy Law No. 105/2016 / QH13, Decree 36/2016 / ND-CP on management of medical equipment, seminars on screening for cardiovascular disease, blood pressure, and diabetes.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In particular, within the framework of the Exhibition, a seminar on "Cancer treatment with immunotherapy and stem cells" will take place with the participation of leading doctors and experts of Vietnam and Japan in the field. Immune and stem cells.</span>', '30 countries attended the largest International Medical Exhibition in Vietnam', 'The event was organized by the Central Center for Health Education and Communication, Vietnam Health Import and Export Joint Stock Company (VIMEDIMEX VN), Vietnam Exhibition and Advertising Joint Stock Company (VIETFAIR).', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '30-countries-attended-the-largest-international-medical-exhibition-in-vietnam', '', '', '2019-01-20 15:35:19', '2019-01-20 15:35:19', '', 0, 'http://medipharm.co/?p=607', 0, 'post', '', 0);
