div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-355-2"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-355-2-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-355-2-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget">This is an annual event of Vietnam''s health sector chaired by Vietnam''s Ministry of Health and Vietnam Ministry of Industry and Trade. The organizational units are: Vietnam Medical Equipment Association, Vietnam Society of Ophthalmology, VIMEDIMEX Medical Pharmaceutical Joint Stock Company (Ministry of Health) and VINEXAD Advertising &amp; Trade Fair JSC (Ministry of Industry and Trade) .\n\nExhibition VIETNAM MEDI-PHARM EXPO 2018 in TP. HO CHI MINH has attracted nearly 400 stores of more than 350 companies from 20 countries and territories such as Australia, France, Germany, Italy, Belgium, Czech, Russia, Belarus, Japan, Korea, Malaysia, Singapore , Thailand, China, Taiwan, Hong Kong, India, Pakistan, Bangladesh and Vietnam showcased products in areas such as medical equipment, supplies and consumables; Pharmaceutical &amp; Pharmaceutical processing and packaging machinery; Hospital equipment; Health care service; Experimental, analytical and environmental equipment; Equipment and pharmaceuticals specialized in dentistry and ophthalmology ...\n\nVIETNAM MEDI-PHARM EXPO 2019 in TP. Ho Chi Minh City will be the place for businesses to advertise and introduce their equipment, machinery and services and products in the most effective way. At the exhibition, businesses have the opportunity to exchange, exchange experiences, seek partners, joint ventures to associate investment projects and purchase products. In addition, the organizers have arranged activities such as: Workshop on introduction of Vietnam medicine and pharmacy market, production and business regulations and policies chaired by departments and agencies of the Ministry of Health; Field trips at pharmaceutical factories or typical hospitals in Ho Chi Minh City. Ho Chi Minh. There are also specialized workshops of exhibitors.\n\nIn order to promote the Exhibition, the advertising and communication work has been planned, prepared and carefully carried out on a large scale. Organizers are expected to issue and send more than 30,000 invitations through such forms as e-mail marketing, delivery by post, fax, direct phone calls to the Enterprise, managers and researchers. , training, hospitals, clinics, health centers and professional officials throughout the country to participate in exhibitions and work visits at the exhibition. Exhibition information is available in specialized newspapers and mass media including television, print, radio and website.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'Overview', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '355-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-21 05:34:50', '2019-01-21 05:34:50', '', 355, 'http://medipharm.co/355-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
